13:["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4","children":"Kalkulyatordan qanday foydalanish"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-sm sm:prose-base max-w-none text-muted-foreground space-y-4","children":[["$","div","0",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Kalkulyator qanday ishlaydi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Kreditni qayta moliyalash — mavjud kreditni to'lash uchun yangi, foydaliroq shartlardagi kredit olish. O'zbekistonda bu xizmat ayniqsa dolzarb: Markaziy bankning 2026-yildagi kalit stavkasi 14% ni tashkil etadi va stavka 20–24% da kredit rasmiylashtirgan ko'plab qarz oluvchilar ortiqcha to'lovni sezilarli kamaytirishi mumkin. Qayta moliyalash kalkulyatori aniq tejash summasini ko'rsatadi va asoslangan qaror qabul qilishga yordam beradi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","1",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash formulasi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Qayta moliyalash bir necha shart bajarilganda foydali: joriy va yangi stavka o'rtasidagi farq kamida 2–3 foiz punkt; kreditning qolgan muddati 1 yildan ortiq; muddatidan oldin to'lash uchun jarimalar yo'q (O'zbekiston qonunchiligiga ko'ra banklar iste'mol kreditlarini muddatidan oldin to'lashni taqiqlash huquqiga ega emas). Qo'shimcha xarajatlarni ham hisobga oling: garov mulkni qayta baholash, yangi bank komissiyasi, sug'urta polisini qayta rasmiylashtirish."}]]}]]}],["$","div","2",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash misoli"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Hisoblash misoli: "}],["$","$La","1",{"href":"/uz/calculator/ipoteka","localeCookie":"$3:props:child